                        <interp inst="t18471025-name-402" type="given" value="EMMA"></interp>EMMA LEE.</persName>
                  </hi> I live at Iver. I went to Mr. Jones' shop at Uxbridge, last Monday, and bought some print, some lining, and unbleached calico—the prisoner served me—I paid him two half-crowns and a sixpence—he gave me a bill which I left behind on the counter—this is it.</p>
